<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.1 (STRIP 1) MACHENGYUAN 8: 171 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-1a.1">成王既封周公二年，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-1a.2">而王厚其任，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-1a.3">乃(厥)訪 {於} [...]【1】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.2 (STRIPS 16, 12, 13) MACHENGYUAN 8: 188, 184-185 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a.1">[...] 之至，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a.2">在周之東，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a.3">乃命之曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a.4">“昔者有神【16】道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a.5">大哉, 沌乎！</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a.6">欲舉之不果 ，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a.7">以進則傷焉 .</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a.8">達【12】是（譴）[抻]之不果，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a.9">毀之不可，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a.10">狀高危，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-2a.11">以澤深【13】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.3 (STRIPS 3, 14) MACHENGYUAN 8: 175, 186 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-3a.1">“[...] 欲明知之.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-3a.2">周公曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-3a.3">“旦之聞之也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-3a.4">各在其身，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-3a.5">而【3】皆見彰于天.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.4 (STRIP 14) MACHENGYUAN 8: 186 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-4a.1">成王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-4a.2">“夫夏繒氏之道，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-4a.3">可以知善否，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-4a.4">可以知亡在，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-4a.5">可謂有道乎?”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.5 (STRIPS 14, 11, 6) MACHENGYUAN 8: 186, 183, 178 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-5a.1">周公曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-5a.2">“是夫【14】先二事之修也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-5a.3">外道之明者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-5a.4">少疏於身，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-5a.5">非天子【11】之正道也.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.6 (STRIPS 6,8,7) MACHENGYUAN 8: 178, 180, 179 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-6a.1">成王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-6a.2">“請問天子之正道?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-6a.3">周公曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-6a.4">“【6】[民]皆欲捨其親而親之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-6a.5">皆欲以其邦就之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-6a.6">是謂【8】天子之正道.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-6a.7">弗朝[招]而自至，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-6a.8">弗審而自周，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-6a.9">弗會[劊]而自斷.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.7 (STRIPS 7, 10) MACHENGYUAN 8: 179, 182 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-7a.1">成王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-7a.2">“請問其事”【7】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-7a.3">[...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-7a.4">而賢者，能以其六藏之守取親焉，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-7a.5">是謂六親之約.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.8 (STRIP 10) MACHENGYUAN 8: 182 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-8a.1">成王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-8a.2">“請問其方?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-8a.3">周[公曰 [...] 【10】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.9 (STRIP 5) MACHENGYUAN 8: 177 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-9a.1">[...] 焉不曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-9a.2">“日彰而冰消乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-9a.3">成王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-9a.4">“嗚呼！道 [...]【5】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.10 (STRIPS 15, 9) MACHENGYUAN 8: 187, 181 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-10a.1">[…] 重殃.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-10a.2">重殃其昌[猖]也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-10a.3">可期而須也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-10a.4">此六者皆逆.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-10a.5">民皆有乖離之心，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-10a.6">而國有相患害之志，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-10a.7">是謂重【15】殃,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-10a.8">重殃 [...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.11 (STRIP 9) MACHENGYUAN 8: 181 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-11a" ed="tls" n="001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-11a.1">持往[皇]明之德其世也【9】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.12 (STRIP 2) MACHENGYUAN 8: 174 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-12a" ed="tls" n="001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-12a.1">王在鎬，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-12a.2">召周公旦曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-12a.3">“嗚呼，敬之哉！</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-12a.4">聞哉 [=在] {昔}【2】[...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGWANGJIFENG 8.46.13 (STRIP 4) MACHENGYUAN 8: 175 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-13a" ed="tls" n="001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-13a.1">伯夷、叔齊 餓而死於雝[=窮]瀆 (=溝瀆)，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-13a.2">不辱其身，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0075_tls_001-13a.3">精【4】[...]</seg></p>

